reviewText: Great Products ... Great Shipping ... Great Amazon Seller . A+++++
MetalBlade put this DVD out it is awesome live stuff from Goatwhore to Cannibal Corposes. Buy this item you will enjoy the live material. I did.

Metal Blade Records has been around since 1983. They filmed this show last year. It has lots of old metal bands such as my favs. HALLOWS EVE (their new album drops soon)
but there is entirely too much 'Job for a cowboy'  and useless screaming scrap.
But I bought it for HALLOWS EVE, nuff said
